  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.text_1": "这是唤魔者附魔室",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.text_2": "它可以将附魔书（复印本）附魔为可以使用的附魔书",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.text_3": "通过经验泵向其输送附魔所需要的经验",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_s_8911d.text_4": "附魔书的总等级越高，所需的经验越多，时间越长",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.header": "鱿鱼打印机",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_1": "这是一个简单的附魔流水线",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_2": "这是鱿鱼打印机",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_3": "在侧面标记一本附魔书...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_4": "它会将下方的书加工为附魔书（复印本）",
  "create_biotech.ponder.squid_printer_scene_1.text_5": "无论是否在工作，打印机都需要输入水来保证鱿鱼存活",
  "create_biotech.ponder.universal_joint.header": "史莱姆万向节",
  "create_biotech.ponder.universal_joint.text_1": "史莱姆万向节可以在相近的任意两个点之间传播应力",
  "create_biotech.ponder.universal_joint.text_2": "以一个节点为中心，另一个节点需要在5×5×5范围内",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.header": "经验泵 输出",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_1": "输出端在没有阻塞时会输出经验球",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_2": "也可以输出到经验储罐，或其他接受经验的容器",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_3": "输出端不能直接将经验转化为物品",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_4": "你需要将经验通入经验母岩...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_s_40666.text_5": "催化成熟的经验簇会自然掉落，它存储的经验值远高于经验颗粒",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.header": "经验泵 输入",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.text_1": "经验泵可以用于在泵两端传递经验",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.text_2": "输入端接受多种形式的经验",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.text_3": "经验球...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.text_4": "经验储罐...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.text_5": "装有经验物品的储物方块...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.text_6": "或者玩家",
  "create_biotech.ponder.experience_pump_scene_1.text_7": "在输入端安装分散网，可以吸引更远范围的经验球",
  "create_biotech.ponder.schrodingers_cat.header": "薛定谔的猫",
  "create_biotech.ponder.schrodingers_cat.text_1": "薛定谔的猫会在其背后随机输出红石信号",
  "create_biotech.ponder.schrodingers_cat.text_2": "其间隔时间和输出模式（持续信号/脉冲信号）可以在侧面配置",
  "create_biotech.ponder.slime_belt_connector.header": "史莱姆传送带",
  "create_biotech.ponder.slime_belt_connector.text_1": "史莱姆传送带可以像一般传送带一样传输物品",
  "create_biotech.ponder.slime_belt_connector.text_2": "不同的是，物品不会在传送带末端被抛出，而是会继续运动到传送带背面",
  "create_biotech.ponder.slime_belt_connector.text_3": "史莱姆传送带还可以竖直传动物品",
  "create_biotech.ponder.slime_belt_connector.text_4": "相连的史莱姆传送带可以形成一个回环",
  "create_biotech.ponder.spider_assembly_table.header": "蜘蛛装配站",
  "create_biotech.ponder.spider_assembly_table.text_1": "蜘蛛装配台可以执行序列装配配方",
  "create_biotech.ponder.spider_assembly_table.text_2": "右键打开界面，在第一行放入装配所需要的机器...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.spider_assembly_table.text_3": "在第二行放入装配所需原料",
  "create_biotech.ponder.spider_assembly_table.text_4": "装配！",
  "create_biotech.ponder.bio_packager_s_fe8b2.header": "生物打包机 捕捉",
  "create_biotech.ponder.bio_packager_s_fe8b2.text_1": "生物打包机会自动提取附着库存中的纸箱，并捕捉被动态结构杀死的生物",
  "create_biotech.ponder.bio_packager_scene_1.header": "生物打包机 释放",
  "create_biotech.ponder.bio_packager_scene_1.text_1": "接入红石信号...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.bio_packager_scene_1.text_2": "生物打包机会从其附着的库存中提取装有生物的纸箱并释放到其上方",
  "create_biotech.ponder.power_belt_connector.header": "动力传送带",
  "create_biotech.ponder.power_belt_connector.text_1": "动力传送带会在有生物在其上方运动时产生应力",
  "create_biotech.ponder.power_belt_connector.text_2": "上方生物运动的越快，产生的转速越高，应力越高",
  "create_biotech.ponder.power_belt_connector.text_3": "多个实体产生的应力会叠加，但是转速不会",
  "create_biotech.ponder.power_belt_connector.text_4": "使用固定的钓竿，让动物为你工作",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_s_29671.header": "恶魂热气球装配站 操纵",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_s_29671.text_1": "使用恶魂驾驶台来操控恶魂热气球",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_s_29671.text_2": "W/S 前后移动",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_s_29671.text_3": "A/D 左右转弯",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_s_29671.text_4": "空格/Shift 上下移动",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_s_29671.text_5": "Ctrl 停止操控",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_s_29671.text_6": "Alt 自动靠近附近未充能的装配站",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_scene_1.header": "恶魂热气球装配站 组装",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_scene_1.text_1": "使用恶魂热气球装配站来组装你的恶魂热气球",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_scene_1.text_2": "使用强力胶粘合你的热气球",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_scene_1.text_3": "使用缓冲垫可以防止结构陷入地下",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_scene_1.text_4": "然后为热气球装配站接入红石",
  "create_biotech.ponder.ghast_hot_air_balloon_assembly_station_scene_1.text_5": "再在装配站上方放一只恶魂",
  "create_biotech.ponder.tag.ponderer_exported": "思索者...",
  "create_biotech.ponder.tag.ponderer_exported.description": "以上思索由模组思索者（Ponderer）制作并导出，了解更多：https://modrinth.com/mod/the-ponderer"
}